Well, I started making this map in curiosidy of how hammer works, ive spent quite a bit of time on it. I really do believe this is a good first timer, just my thoughts though.

I worked with the lighting a little bit, used cubemaps, threw in some props, fishes. I learned quite a bit from just making this map, and with the tips gattsu had givin me.

I just ask, that you guys give your honest opinion on the map. Thank you.
